Package com.microblink.recognizers.blinkocr

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DocumentClassifier
    Classifier that is used to classify documents based on data extracted from detector's decoding info fields.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlinkOCRRecognitionResult
    Represents recognition result produced by BlinkOCR recognizer which was configured with BlinkOCRRecognizerSettings.
    BlinkOCRRecognizerSettings
    Represents settings for generic OCR recognizer used for scanning segments.
